milestones.description: Bruce Edgar and Martin Crowe's 130-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 126 between Glenn Turner and Geoff Howarth
Kapil Dev and Ravi Shastri's 87-run partnership is IND's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 73 between Yashpal Sharma and Roger Binny
This is the highest match aggregate (522) involving teams New Zealand & India in ODIs
Gavaskar has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (68) for IND, going past Kapil Dev
